::Cerberus/Fame/Obitus::

    They were all looking at a map of Earth, they=
 noticed that they could get from one continent to another very easily. The=
y planned the route. Cerberus made a list of what the bots would need and w=
ent in to the destroyed base to find the weapon room.
    He found it after=
 walking through much of the base. There was still a very good stash of wea=
pons there. "Magmatron would have never realized what this place was capabl=
e of. Once I return to Cybertron I will teach him that lesson. He really sh=
ouldn't have left me for dead."
    Fame had overheard this and was surpris=
ed. Magmatron hadn't sent Cerberus. If anything, he had tried to kill him, =
but had failed. He wanted to know more about this so called Emissary of Mag=
matron.
